{"tid":1218551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」 關於星期日遊行，去定唔去？","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T17:55:20.000Z","uid":58307,"like":231,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"21f4e8737f593b31fb1b118a87e6547779e8e4e2","tid":1218551,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩飲左幾支紅酒醉醉地開post.<br />\n想講係依家開始有post叫人星期日唔好出，原因都離不開話怕人數少之類。收皮啦。（好多五毛開工架依排，邊句真邊句假要自己識分）人數多少決定贏局！<br />\n<br />\n身邊d朋友大部分都講定星期日會出，完全無人話唔會出，唔好因爲某d人講某d原來就放棄自己原先ge理念同想法。 做自己認為對的事！<br />\n<br />\n香港人！無得輸架啦！ 黃背心都幾個月啦！要堅持✊<br />\n唔好辜負左班義士。"},{"pid":"c1149510f1174854dc185f05879e2cf134689d0b","tid":1218551,"uid":138886,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"8877bd9d749564d0294a8ce3a78c5b9778134084","tid":1218551,"uid":171389,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"去，無選擇"},{"pid":"d4252f4d48fe6f04b9a01ac14f2a8018936b7b29","tid":1218551,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:07:05.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"d2e9b10ca36de65f11c6db70a45a5ace22b7a248","tid":1218551,"uid":258566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d8b9cd22f874ac6800f86a0845ead965e40db45","tid":1218551,"uid":230306,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"老閪都去！"},{"pid":"800e8b37cd71d572e7ad5e0e929d579426f3a9d9","tid":1218551,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:16:11.000Z","msg":"俾人屌屎忽都要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0e4db175c292faa0c2e140f99c87e83341629f","tid":1218551,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"bf59c44da72d3e71a69f4902503d882a0990ac52","tid":1218551,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r